{"id": 2200, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都是怎么消耗无所事事的时间，好让自己踏实一点的？", "description": "你也有空白时间焦虑症吗？宁可花时间做点无谓的事也决不能闲着。", "record_count": 2602, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180228114414Qibt2gupfO4jDGvM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-01T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 268032, "content": "重温老友记 没事就点开一集看", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093132}, {"id": 268288, "content": "看三国，读新闻，思考公司的事情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276027}, {"id": 268034, "content": "手机挂着手游，拿着kindle看书，总感觉不用多久就会有人找，但往往一坐就是一下午?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274716}, {"id": 268290, "content": "玩手机呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276063}, {"id": 268035, "content": "看书，听付费音频，观察周围的人，或者思考人生?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461690}, {"id": 268291, "content": "手机里下了好多学习看书的app,他们一直都被遗忘", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276056}, {"id": 268037, "content": "You know take snap ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223465}, {"id": 268293, "content": "打开手机，把各种APP打开一遍……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583318}, {"id": 268295, "content": "不想学习，想玩手机\n但是强迫自己看书，然后发呆(´-ι_-｀)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276110}, {"id": 268296, "content": "一边做家务一边听网课", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275340}, {"id": 268041, "content": "老丰富了，战地1、战地4、彩虹六号围攻、STEEP……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271667}, {"id": 268042, "content": "从来没有骗过别人，回头看居然发现我骗自己居然这么厉害", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273844}, {"id": 268043, "content": "收拾房间，丢东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274759}, {"id": 268044, "content": "洗澡还非得听个podcast", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671593}, {"id": 268300, "content": "不停的刷着视频播放器，找季数比较多的美剧看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276138}, {"id": 268045, "content": "B站废着 ... ...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233801}, {"id": 269069, "content": "看书，听有声书。\n瑜伽，静静地发呆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280310}, {"id": 268046, "content": "告诉自己：我在认真的发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244885}, {"id": 268047, "content": "发呆 逗龟 睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146095}, {"id": 268048, "content": "吃鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132851}, {"id": 268049, "content": "电影，新闻，财经，看创业，找新鲜项目，养生。感觉30岁虚度了，一事无成，慢性自杀没区别", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001616}, {"id": 268050, "content": "想着自己该做点什么，然后想着想着开始打游戏，看手机随便乱刷。游戏打完了还有时间就各种发呆看剧了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124303}, {"id": 270354, "content": "吃超蝙粮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284670}, {"id": 268051, "content": "睁眼就第二天了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274798}, {"id": 267796, "content": "首选手机，其次是电视，这俩都没有，那就只好看书了", "image": null, "praise_count": 186, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273753}, {"id": 268052, "content": "边刷牙，边找衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354932}, {"id": 268308, "content": "画画，打草稿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819803}, {"id": 267797, "content": "看好奇心呗", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235338}, {"id": 268053, "content": "闲不下来，总在刷剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274808}, {"id": 268309, "content": "放空", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276288}, {"id": 268054, "content": "1.打开想学习的东西 研究一会 开始玩手机 2.闲聊喝酒 3.总是看一很多感觉很励志的鸡汤 故事 其实看完并不见得有长进", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257906}, {"id": 267799, "content": "打炮", "image": null, "praise_count": 109, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180628}, {"id": 268055, "content": "做操", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 268311, "content": "涂鸦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251032}, {"id": 267800, "content": "洗碗、化妆、打扫的时候放着有声书或播客听", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75414}, {"id": 268056, "content": "发呆", "image": "img/option/option/20180302072632y7exw4Xq6tfLdSVR", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274825}, {"id": 267801, "content": "吃鸡\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111636}, {"id": 268057, "content": "看远处山上的电杆  ", "image": "img/option/option/20180302072851LOEnPgCKRzXhl0GD", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274825}, {"id": 268058, "content": "睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243211}, {"id": 268314, "content": "煲老剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869910}, {"id": 267803, "content": "打开一本书 开始玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747017}, {"id": 268059, "content": "发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194263}, {"id": 267804, "content": "长胖让我踏实。体重让我踏实。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871118}, {"id": 268060, "content": "当然虎扑啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272675}, {"id": 268316, "content": "学习",